{"tid":1154162,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男人都很垃圾的","createTime":"2019-05-14T05:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T12:00:08.000Z","uid":56702,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd39a4c2cd5cf5f35710a9c236421a7e2bc84a8","tid":1154162,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"有個女仔對自己好少少就心軟，然後另一個女仔對自己好少少又心軟。<br />\n<br />\n即係咁<br />\n<br />\n起初A女好靚好正其實無乜期望，點知A女對自己好少少就衝，衝到就覺得咁難得都食到就唔好辜負人，要好好對人。<br />\n<br />\n點知到A女對自己差少少就動搖，之後出現B女，B女都有A女八成咁正，而B女對自己好少少就搞埋B女，內心就賴A女對自己唔好，所以就覺得B女更好而糊塗咗，但如果B女對自己比A女對自己好啲，咪同B女一齊囉。<br />\n<br />\n其實如果之後又有C女出現對自己好少少，都會搞埋。DEFGHIJLMNOPQ都係咁<br />\n<br />\n我唔tag人啦，個個都唔認衰仔，但到時咪又係咁。<br />\n<br />\n男人呢樣野真係靠唔住。"},{"pid":"728f154344c3ab71f55ab847b669a71fa0182c9f","tid":1154162,"uid":253005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94b56b3c9a567e247a2a0846f5fe33f364f83ac8","tid":1154162,"uid":4736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"最後Z女有A女幾多成？ 求解"},{"pid":"8205db3c6d50a9a9ea3e5b8e84ddfeff53df63ca","tid":1154162,"uid":229548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪A女？"},{"pid":"8d1a7355d8b4460f66c9681239111f59e497deb9","tid":1154162,"uid":194403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"樓主錯曬...唔係所有男人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151d0411ba8bb73caeabfc8dd994a0df25dce17e","tid":1154162,"uid":130438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"上少啲連登啦"},{"pid":"a7e1697332395dc5fddc13f5c0200882caa15049","tid":1154162,"uid":97604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾係冇性別之分"},{"pid":"48cc67d6b697a0282190f21cff96e7f737950b9a","tid":1154162,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06